dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Juan Henderson. May I have your name please?
Hello Juan, my name is Ann Kelly.
Nice to meet you, Ann. Could you please provide me with your date of birth in the format day, month, year separately?
Sure, my date of birth is zero four, zero eight, one nine eight five.
Thank you, Ann. I also need your home address. Could you please spell it out for me?
Of course, my home address is tango hotel r o m e o four seven, victor india c a n a d a.
Great, thank you for providing that information, Ann. Is there anything specific I can assist you with today regarding your auto insurance policy?
I have a question about my policy coverage.
I'd be happy to help with that. Please provide me with your policy number so I can look up the details.
Thank you for your time, Ann. If you need any further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day.
